{{Top|leg}}
The '''thunder drum''' was a large, two-[[Meter/Legends|meter]]-high percussion instrument that required two people to operate it by swinging huge mallets at the drum heads.

Traditionally a [[Weequay/Legends|Weequay]] instrument, thunder drums were often found in [[Sriluurian]] monasteries devoted to [[Am-Shak/Legends|Am-Shak]], god of thunder. [[Ak-rev/Legends|Ak-rev]] of the [[Max Rebo Band/Legends|Max Rebo Band]] was a masterful thunder drum player.

